{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "杂贺 第2话 来自暗影的质疑",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "糟了！这是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "这样下去火会烧遍整座山的！\\n必须以火制火——哈啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "要以逆火相冲，\\n灭掉蔓延的山火才行！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "杂贺大人！您没事吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "牛头天王也逃出来了啊。\\n阿迪斯呢？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "您冲出去之后，\\n他也追着您跑出去了……\\n两位没在一起吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "难道他还留在锻造工坊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "拜托你继续在这里灭山火。\\n在下回锻造工坊一趟。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "锻造工坊已经是一片火海！\\n您只身回去太危险了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "道理在下都懂。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "杂贺大人！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "阿迪斯！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿迪斯",
            "context": "杂贺……你来救我了！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "你被倒塌的柱子压住了吗。\\n在下这就帮你挪开……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "唔！\\n没法轻易抬动吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿迪斯",
            "context": "火势更凶猛了！\\n别管我了，你快逃！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "不，还不能放弃！\\n在下不能丢下你逃跑！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿迪斯",
            "context": "这样下去你也会死的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "在下怎么能扔下你\\n自己苟且偷生！\\n唔噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "柱子挪开了！快逃到外面！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿迪斯",
            "context": "杂贺，感激不尽……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "总算是把山火抑制住了。\\n刚才的爆炸到底怎么回事啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "是用油和符咒设计的爆破。\\n估计是为了处理掉这座废弃的\\n锻造工坊而事先准备好的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "用铳狙击我们的那个人影\\n应该就是来安排爆破的\\n骸众成员吧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿迪斯",
            "context": "我姑且把在锻造工坊发现的地图\\n带出来了，可光靠这个想锁定\\n他们的去向有点难啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "铳是先填充魔力再将其释放的武器，\\n如果他们要以铳为原型来造武器，\\n应该会需要大量魔力。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "大量魔力……啊！\\n二位请看这个。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "这是之前晴明大人\\n让式鬼绘制的南方大陆\\n龙脉泉的地图。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "要建锻造工坊的话，\\n应该是离矿区和龙脉泉\\n都近的地方最合适。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "那根据这两张地图来推测，\\n最有可能的地方应该是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "南格拉斯迪亚大陆\\n奎因贝尔",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110364_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯瑟琳",
            "context": "住宿我已经安排好了，\\n你们只要报上我的名字\\n就可以入住。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110363_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤金",
            "context": "阿迪斯你们明天\\n是要去调查这前面的矿山吧？\\n有什么需要帮忙准备的尽管开口。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿迪斯",
            "context": "多谢，算我欠你们一个人情。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110364_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯瑟琳",
            "context": "话说尤金，我听说你又过上\\n三餐光吃牛轧糖的生活了？\\n这对身体可不好！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110363_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤金",
            "context": "啊？你现在说这个干嘛？\\n而且跟你又没关系……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "记得你们二位……\\n是青梅竹马来着？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110363_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤金",
            "context": "诶？啊、嗯。是没错……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110364_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯瑟琳",
            "context": "那又怎么了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "不……没什么。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "杂贺大人有很要好的\\n青梅竹马吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "为什么会这么想？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "您看着尤金大人他们的时候\\n表情很柔和。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "在下和妻子百代从小就相识。\\n刚才是因为想起了这个。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿迪斯",
            "context": "你老婆是个什么样的人？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "在下无父无母，\\n小时候即便在下行为粗鲁，\\n她也不畏惧与在下交谈。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "在下拜入她祖父门下学武\\n也是因为她的劝说，\\n说有热衷的事物也许能排解孤独。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "她很稳重又善解人意，\\n在下因她的温柔而得到了救赎。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "你很珍视她吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "是啊……所以，\\n她去世时在下根本无法想象\\n没有她的人生要怎么活。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "所以在下才听信了骸众的花言巧语，\\n结果还亲手把师父……\\n也就是百代和八千代的祖父……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01",
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "二人",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "在下害死师父的时候才幡然醒悟，\\n自己的所作所为剥夺了他人的\\n重要之人，是罪无可赦的行为。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "在下为了偿还之前的罪孽，\\n会竭尽所能。\\n这就是今后在下的生存之道。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "所以为了不让骸众的武器\\n造成新的伤亡，无论如何\\n也要端掉他们的锻造工坊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "二人",
            "context": "好！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01",
                "110310_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "百代",
            "context": "杂贺……杂贺……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "百代！是你吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "百代",
            "context": "我已经时日无多了，\\n所以有一事相求。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "你在哪里！？百代！？\\n你快现身啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "百代",
            "context": "杂贺，替我……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "百代！\\n果然是梦啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "心还在怦怦跳……\\n看来是睡不着了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "那个梦……在下想起来了，\\n那是百代卧病在床时说的话。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "那个时候\\n她想告诉在下的是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "刚才的铳声是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "你的所作所为不可原谅。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "你是……在锻造工坊的\\n那个骸众成员！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "你享受着新生活，可那只是在逃避。\\n你过去不肯正视现实，\\n现在则不肯正视自己。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "你懂什么？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "不懂的是你才对。\\n再怎么赎罪，死去的人也不会复生。\\n竟然还妄想活下去，太恬不知耻了吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "住口！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "杂贺大人，\\n我还想您怎么不见了，\\n原来是在这里啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "是骸众！还拿着铳！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "您说什么？在哪里！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "你没看到吗！？\\n敌人就在眼前……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210136_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "牛头天王",
            "context": "一个人都没有啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110389_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "杂贺",
            "context": "怎么会……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}